data.description: Are you looking for a property that is close to everything and offers some fantastic features that you rarely find? The exterior of this home offers those features to include a beautifully appointed covered front porch with wood accented ceiling and 2 ceiling fans , a 36x30 ft 3 bay barn/outbuilding/accessory building with 6 inch concrete slab, 2 gorgeous 10x10 handbuilt doors as well as a third 8x10 sliding door, wired and ready for the buyer that wants to create a workshop, add a lift for the person that likes to do auto work, some additional parking, a hang out space or amazing storage space as well as a unique gazebo a/k/a the cook shack-ready for your grilling and entertaining or just perfect for relaxing with a morning coffee, unwinding at the end of the day or watching your favorite sporting event, movie or tv show and don't miss the fantastic firepit. All three structures offer metal roofing. Did I mention so many places to park your vehicles including a rear carport and loads of additional parking room. Inside you will find a phenomenal sized primary bedroom with walk in closet that offers two entrances-one that leads direct to the living room, nice sized eat in kitchen with wonderful wood countertops, wood look tile floor, ample cabinet space including a pantry cabinet, range, vent hood and dishwasher, spacious laundry room, hall bath offers combo tub shower, leathered granite countertop and tile floor, two secondary bedrooms-one of which has a full bath that offers an accessible sink, shower and commode. All of this sits on 1.92 acres. A portion of the yard is fenced and offers zoysia grass in that area. This home is located less than 5 miles from downtown Senoia, within 5 miles of Elementary, Middle and High Schools as well as Coweta Charter and quick access to all Newnan and Peachtree City have to offer.
